 * - OpenVINS: Visual-Inertial Odometry for camera-based navigation
 * - FAST-LIO: LiDAR-Inertial Odometry for precise positioning
 * - IMU: Inertial Measurement Unit for attitude and angular velocity
 * - GPS: Global Positioning System for absolute position reference
 * - PX4 Odometry: Flight controller internal state estimates
